  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/desktops/\" rel=\"tag\">桌面产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/02/28/fifa-14-is-now-available-for-windows-phone/\"><img alt=\"FIFA 14 for Windows Phone\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/4e0683a162950db691bbf40e7b6b167b/fifa-14-windows-phone.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 339px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n世界杯开赛前想玩玩 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/24/fifa-14-android-ios/\">FIFA 14</a> 过瘾，可惜手中只有一台 Windows Phone？这在今天之后就不再是个问题了。EA 早些时候已将这款免费游戏放上了 Marketplace，让 Windows Phone 玩家也能享受和 iOS、Android 用户一样的足球乐趣。当然，之前在另两个平台上出现的购买球队分数、特殊比赛模式（比如经理模式或 Kick Off 模式等）等功能也在 Windows Phone 版本中杯保留了下来，想玩的朋友去下载试试吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/28/fifa-14-is-now-available-for-windows-phone/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/windowsphone/archive/2014/02/28/fifa-14-now-available-in-the-windows-phone-store.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Windows Phone Blog</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/s?appid=0ed6989b-5cb9-4b70-a58b-536c0dce36b2\" target=\"_blank\">Windows Phone Store</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/28/fifa-14-is-now-available-for-windows-phone/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20840668/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/28/fifa-14-is-now-available-for-windows-phone/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
